{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act18side", "eventName": "塵影餘音", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "LE-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "昇華之夜", "storyInfo": "一行人在音樂廳中發現了格特魯德設置的法術擴散裝置。格特魯德現身，勸誘黑鍵不成後，選擇了動手。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "28_g5_czernyhome", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不在？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生已經出去好一會兒了。", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "出去了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是為了收治中毒的感染者的問題，要去和夕照區之外的醫院交涉......", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorknob"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，怎麼樣，那些醫院——", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勉強談下來了兩家最大的，合約已經簽好，其他的......實在是不行了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可羅德島和醫院簽過協定！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也在啊。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒用的。羅德島和那些醫院的合約僅限礦石病本身引起的症狀，他們有充足的理由不收治因中毒而倒下的感染者。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管怎麼說，先生好歹談下了兩家醫院，應該足夠了吧？", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，夠了，當然夠了！我用自己手裡全部的版權做抵押，他們背後的財團當然覺得夠了！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道您——把自己的版權轉讓給了那家財團？！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，不光以前的版權，連明天音樂會錄音的發行權我都賣給他們了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我可以從零開始了......咳、咳。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......咳！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.3}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_489_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，先生？！", "name": "烏爾蘇拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_489_1#3$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您醒了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......嗯。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生，您在出門的時候沒做任何防護措施，對不對？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說那些源石蟲散發出來的臭氣？合約能早一秒簽下來都是好的，我出門時沒考慮這些。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您絕對不能再像今天這樣莽撞了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“不能再”？也就是說，我還有一段時間好活？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有我在呢。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，身體一垮下來，看醫生也覺得順眼多了。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#11$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你，芙蓉。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#8$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我應該做的。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倒是黑鍵，你怎麼一句話都不說？難道是覺得現在夕照區太危險，想退出了？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我可告訴你，到了現在這一步，音樂會我無論如何也要辦好，不要想臨陣脫逃的事。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要想臨陣脫逃......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）他現在能受得了嗎？", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）稍等一等吧......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來不是要退出音樂會？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，不是要退出音樂會......", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#3$2"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黑鍵，你一緊張就喜歡重複別人的話，我從一開始就能看得出來。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#2$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼話就說吧，我倒要看看，都現在這副樣子了，還有什麼事是我受不了的。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳——咳咳咳！！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼先生，水、水！", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$pourwater", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 150.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glass_break", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳，格特魯德這個——這個！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有你，你怎麼想的，居然能同意這種計畫？虧我還覺得你算是可造之才，你就想用音樂表達這種東西？一場陰謀？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是這個意思——", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼不是？你一開始不是老老實實答應那個瘋女人了嗎？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "車爾尼，我記得你說過，就算是刻骨的憎恨，只要能用合適的技法表達出來，那也是純粹的音樂。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是說過，然後呢？你想表達什麼？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......說實話，現在我已經覺得自己當時的想法很可笑了。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#7$2"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我想追求的，無非是自由而已。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#2$2"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——自由，對自由的渴望，是吧？", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#1$2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要把它用音樂表達出來，你還差得遠呢！", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#3$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經深刻地感受到這一點了，否則我才不來找你。", "name": "黑鍵"}, "figure_art": "avg_4046_ebnhlz_1#6$2"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#7$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走吧。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走？去哪？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還能是哪，音樂廳啊。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前格特魯德就耍花招把我擋在音樂廳休息室外面，現在我倒要看看，她在裡面搞了什麼名堂。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可您的身體......", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其在這裡被他和那女人氣死，我還不如去看看他們到底在搞什麼鬼。", "name": "車爾尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_4047_pianst_1#6$1"